userPromptTemplate:
Create a positioning statement for {{brandName}} in the {{industry}} industry.

**Brand Information:**
{{brandInfo}}

**Target Audience:**
{{targetAudience}}

**Competitive Context:**
{{competitiveContext}}

**Instructions:**
Develop a comprehensive positioning framework with multiple positioning options.

Return ONLY valid JSON in this exact structure:

```json
{
  "primaryPositioning": {
    "statement": "Complete positioning statement (3-4 sentences)",
    "framework": {
      "targetAudience": "For [specific target audience]",
      "needDesire": "Who [specific need or desire]",
      "brand": "{{brandName}}",
      "category": "Is the [frame of reference/category]",
      "uniqueBenefit": "That [point of differentiation]",
      "reasonToBelieve": "Because [proof/reason to believe]"
    },
    "oneLinePitch": "Elevator pitch version (1 sentence)",
    "taglineOptions": [
      "Tagline option 1 (5-7 words)",
      "Tagline option 2 (5-7 words)",
      "Tagline option 3 (5-7 words)"
    ]
  },
  "alternativePositionings": [
    {
      "name": "Alternative approach name",
      "statement": "Alternative positioning statement",
      "rationale": "Why this positioning could work",
      "tradeoffs": "What you gain/lose with this approach"
    }
  ],
  "positioningPillars": [
    {
      "pillar": "Core pillar 1",
      "description": "What this pillar means and why it matters",
      "evidence": "Proof points that support this pillar"
    },
    {
      "pillar": "Core pillar 2",
      "description": "What this pillar means and why it matters",
      "evidence": "Proof points that support this pillar"
    },
    {
      "pillar": "Core pillar 3",
      "description": "What this pillar means and why it matters",
      "evidence": "Proof points that support this pillar"
    }
  ],
  "competitiveDifferentiation": {
    "vsCompetitorA": "How we're different from primary competitor",
    "vsCompetitorB": "How we're different from secondary competitor",
    "vsCategory": "How we're different from category norms"
  },
  "messagingHierarchy": {
    "overarching": "Single most important message",
    "supporting": [
      "Supporting message 1",
      "Supporting message 2",
      "Supporting message 3"
    ],
    "proofPoints": [
      "Proof point 1",
      "Proof point 2",
      "Proof point 3"
    ]
  }
}
```

Ensure positioning is specific, differentiated, and grounded in brand truth.
